caption.p: Cryo-TEM images are presented for spongosomes ( A) without baicalin (BAI) or Brucea javanica oil (BJO), ( B) with BAI only, and ( C) with BAI and BJO; ( D) Encapsulation efficiency (EE) and drug-loading (DL) values of the spongosomes containing BAI only or both BAI and BJO after different storage time periods postfabrication; ( E) In vitro release profiles of BAI in phosphate-buffered saline (PBS) for spongosomes containing BAI only or both BAI and BJO, as compared to free BAI. Adapted with permission from [ 80].
